data.title: Fed Chair Jerome Powell Speech: Bitcoin Climbs as December Rate Cut Odds Waver
data.description: Bitcoin saw a slight relief rebound as Fed Chair Jerome Powell did not address the economy or monetary policy in prepared remarks at Stanford University.
